  <brief_title>Drug Interaction Study to Asses Multiple Doses of ZD4054 (Zibotentan)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Open-label, Crossover, Phase I Study to Assess the Effect of Multiple Oral Doses of ZD4054 (Zibotentan) on the Pharmacokinetics of a CYP450 3A Probe (Midazolam) in Healthy Male Subjects</official_title>
