  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to to assess the effect of multiple oral doses of ZD4054
      (Zibotentan) on the pharmacokinetics of a CYP450 3A Probe (midazolam) in healthy male
      subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
